title: Bodybuilding - Tom Platz - Documentary video
description:
This is a video of Tom Platz in the UK.  It's a look at the man behind the man and, you have his opinion on things, reflection on the past, present and future.

This will certainly paint him in many different lights and, it does have a great deal of surprises in it.

I did find the editting a bit jarring (could be that is how it was meant to be filmed).  However, it puts Platz out there for you to see the man behind the quads.

It runs nearly 2 hrs (1hr57mins).

More videos to come, please help seed
